data.title: Marines TV
data.meta_description: Marines with Tactical Readiness and Training Platoon (TRT), Marine Logistics Group Headquarters, 3rd Marine Logistics Group, trained at Jungle Warfare Training Center,  Okinawa, Japan July 25, 2018. The Marines conducted attacks on known enemy positions using Special Effects Small Arms Marking System rounds to maintain tactical proficiency within a combat environment.  (U.S. Marine Corps video by Cpl. Joshua Pinkney)
